---
title: Buttered Rosemary Strip Steak with a Wedge Salad and Thyme-Roasted Potatoes
description: A steakhouse-worthy meal is totally do-able at home when you’ve got some top-notch ingredients. Which is why we’ve put a beautiful strip steak at the center of this meal, then surrounded it with classy accompaniments like herbed potatoes and a wedge salad with creamy dressing. It’s the sort of thing that feels like it was put together by a master grill chef, except this time, that chef is you.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/buttered-rosemary-strip-steak-5c1fd4b4.jpg
